01:02:29.612 --> 01:02:32.410
Sun-young! He got away.

01:03:05.648 --> 01:03:06.580
Eun-soo!

01:03:24.667 --> 01:03:25.599
Seon-young

01:03:27.870 --> 01:03:31.806
Was it so hard to follow
my instructions?

01:03:34.811 --> 01:03:38.804
