Where is my hero right now?

01:07:03.519 --> 01:07:04.747
Are you listening to me?

01:07:06.655 --> 01:07:11.752
Heroes sometimes suffer
at the weight of their fate.

01:07:13.529 --> 01:07:17.465
But, it's that suffering
makes them stronger.

01:07:19.935 --> 01:07:22.460
Where is my hero right now?

01:07:22.538 --> 01:07:23.562
Are you listening to me?

01:07:25.141 --> 01:07:27.371
He's using the term partner

01:07:27.443 --> 01:07:31.174
he probably wants recognition
from his object of obsession.

01:07:31.247 --> 01:07:35.980
I don't want to see these
psycho killers even in the movies

01:07:38.554 --> 01:07:40.579
Sun-young is a victim, too.

01:07:40.656 --> 01:07:42.180
Stop connecting her to the case.

01:07:44.360 --> 01:07:48.091
I don't want to see these
psycho killers even in the movies.

01:07:59.909 --> 01:08:00.841
What!

01:08:00.910 --> 01:08:03.037
You'd better turn on the television.

01:08:03.112 --> 01:08:06.878
The suspect just sent us
a video clip of himself

01:08:06.949 --> 01:08:11.511
Reporter Jang Seok-hyun
has the exclusive.

01:08:11.587 --> 01:08:17.752
Every Saturday, this is the
quiz corner where you participate.

01:08:17.827 --> 01:08:20.057
We have a caller on hold...
Hello, 'Travis'?

01:08:20.729 --> 01:08:22.662
Hello...?

01:08:23.631 --> 01:08:24.758
Are you ready?

01:08:26.335 --> 01:08:32.171
In front of me, there is a girl
that needs my help.

01:08:32.241 --> 01:08:39.078
The poor girl is living in hell
because of her scumbag pimp.

01:08:40.049 --> 01:08:46.283
And, I have her pimp who is
lower than a scumbag.

