01:08:56.665 --> 01:08:59.792
Is it from Taxi driver?

01:08:59.868 --> 01:09:01.234
The final shootout scene, right?

01:09:02.705 --> 01:09:05.799
Travis kills the pimp
and saves lris.

01:09:05.875 --> 01:09:06.841
Where is everybody?

01:09:09.011 --> 01:09:11.444
And is hailed as a hero
in the press.

01:09:12.915 --> 01:09:16.442
Do you agree with that?

01:09:17.819 --> 01:09:20.755
Travis put his beliefs into action.

01:09:21.423 --> 01:09:26.759
He might be the man we need
in this time of rampant immorality

01:09:28.631 --> 01:09:29.461
Well, l...

01:09:29.532 --> 01:09:31.055
couldn't agree more.

01:09:38.340 --> 01:09:39.272
What is this?

01:09:40.042 --> 01:09:41.270
How was that?

01:09:41.343 --> 01:09:45.279
You scared me.

01:09:45.346 --> 01:09:47.679
Is this being aired?

01:09:48.651 --> 01:09:50.778
It's from our show

01:09:50.853 --> 01:09:53.582
When did you get that?

01:09:53.656 --> 01:09:55.681
You can't just show that
on a public channel!

01:09:55.758 --> 01:09:57.487
We were blackmailed, too.

01:09:57.960 --> 01:10:00.292
The suspect sent us the message

01:10:00.362 --> 01:10:03.388
that if we don't release this clip
there will be another murder

01:10:03.465 --> 01:10:04.193
The murder victim in the video
was identified as Kim Tae-soo

01:10:04.266 --> 01:10:05.164
He threatened to kill the kids

01:10:05.234 --> 01:10:11.798
who made the news in 2006 for
his involvement in human-trafficking.

01:10:11.874 --> 01:10:13.205
He was released on the grounds
of insufficient evidence

01:10:13.275 --> 01:10:15.106
Sentenced innocent
by lack of evidence

01:10:15.177 --> 01:10:18.977
whether there is any justice
in our society.

01:10:19.048 --> 01:10:22.108
Ko Sun-young who was
the newscaster at the time...

01:10:22.184 --> 01:10:25.085
Ms. Ko, how do you feel right now?

01:10:25.154 --> 01:10:26.212
Please, just one word!

01:10:26.288 --> 01:10:28.916
Was the voice on the tape yours?

01:10:30.092 --> 01:10:31.116
It was.

01:10:33.896 --> 01:10:36.023
How do you feel about
Han Dong-soo?

01:10:40.703 --> 01:10:41.635
He...

01:10:46.108 --> 01:10:48.633
He killed criminals.

01:10:48.711 --> 01:10:49.643
I think...

01:10:53.616 --> 01:10:55.846
It was a heroic act.

01:10:58.020 --> 01:10:59.453
Are you listening to me, Han?

01:10:59.521 --> 01:11:02.081
Come on out and talk to me!

01:11:02.157 --> 01:11:03.283
Tell me what you want!

01:11:08.264 --> 01:11:09.288
What do you think you're doing?

01:11:10.065 --> 01:11:12.499
He's a psycho threatening
to kill your kids!

01:11:12.568 --> 01:11:14.695
This is what he wants.

01:11:14.770 --> 01:11:18.706
He's a psycho who
believes he is a hero.

01:11:19.775 --> 01:11:21.208
He'll call me again.

01:11:38.694 --> 01:11:39.524
Eun-soo?

01:11:45.601 --> 01:11:47.432
One more time, baby.

01:11:50.706 --> 01:11:53.038
Can I consider
that as your recognition?

01:11:57.913 --> 01:12:01.076
Yes. Isn't that what you want?

01:12:02.051 --> 01:12:04.884
But, you're too late.

01:12:05.554 --> 01:12:07.488
I've already killed them.

01:12:07.556 --> 01:12:08.580
Liar!

01:12:10.959 --> 01:12:12.392
You're a hero.

01:12:12.461 --> 01:12:14.986
A hero would never do
such a thing

01:12:17.066 --> 01:12:21.366
Officers, have you finished
tracking the location?

01:12:21.437 --> 01:12:23.405
Come and collect the bodies.

01:12:23.472 --> 01:12:25.497
Han Dong-soo!

01:12:25.574 --> 01:12:28.099
I'm turning myself in.

01:12:28.177 --> 01:12:28.905
Han Dong-soo!

01:12:29.678 --> 01:12:30.337
Do we have his location?

01:12:30.412 --> 01:12:32.312
Get everybody over there now!

01:12:32.381 --> 01:12:34.611
And, request for a backup!

01:12:34.683 --> 01:12:38.710
My kids... they're alive,
aren't they?

01:12:50.499 --> 01:12:57.029
Ms. Ko, the sky is white
and clouds are black today.

01:12:58.507 --> 01:12:59.633
Come meet me. Hurry.

01:13:02.945 --> 01:13:04.173
Go! Go!

01:13:22.765 --> 01:13:25.199
All hell broke loose here.

01:13:25.267 --> 01:13:28.293
Where the hell are you?

01:13:28.370 --> 01:13:29.098
Get your ass over here, now!

01:13:29.171 --> 01:13:30.103
Yes, sir!

01:13:32.674 --> 01:13:35.700
I gotta go back to the station.

01:13:36.779 --> 01:13:37.711
Will you be okay?

01:13:38.480 --> 01:13:39.412
I'm okay.

01:13:42.484 --> 01:13:43.815
Come with us, ma'am.

01:13:45.687 --> 01:13:46.619
I'll take my car.

01:13:52.494 --> 01:13:54.826
- Keep closely behind her.
- Yes, sir.

01:13:59.701 --> 01:14:00.668
Let's go!

01:14:05.541 --> 01:14:06.974
Her car just started off.

01:14:16.051 --> 01:14:19.680
You should've sent out
a substitute program

01:14:19.755 --> 01:14:21.780
I don't believe we should do
that in this situation.

01:14:21.857 --> 01:14:23.882
What situation?

01:14:25.060 --> 01:14:28.086
Get your ass in the studio. Now!

01:14:28.163 --> 01:14:29.494
Yes, sir.

01:14:31.266 --> 01:14:32.790
We have exclusive breaking news?

01:14:32.868 --> 01:14:40.297
I have the fax that Han Dong-soo
sent to Ko sun-young tonight.

01:14:40.375 --> 01:14:40.898
Son of a bitch!

01:14:40.976 --> 01:14:44.309
In the fax, there is a playlist
of songs that Han put together

