Detective Cho!

01:16:14.236 --> 01:16:15.168
Who is that?!

01:16:17.773 --> 01:16:19.172
I did exactly as you told me.

01:16:19.942 --> 01:16:21.068
Now, where are the kids?

01:16:21.143 --> 01:16:24.476
Don't worry about them.
