She gave us the slip.

01:16:41.263 --> 01:16:43.891
Were following her to the west.

01:16:43.966 --> 01:16:45.797
Find out who she is.
And, get an aerial backup.

01:16:45.867 --> 01:16:46.891
Yes, sir!

01:16:46.969 --> 01:16:48.596
Hello! This is Han Dong-soo.

01:16:50.072 --> 01:16:56.011
I'm currently moving in a car
